steps.name: Click on 'New Item' on the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
Click on the 'Delete Job' link on the Folder page and go to Main Page
Click on the 'Yes' button on the DeletePage
Check if 'Welcome' is displayed on Main page
